quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  2,275,Those charge usury est same position prout those controlled de devil's influence Hoc est they claim ut usury est same prout commerce. Deus permits commerce prohibits usury. Sic whoever heeds hoc commandment his Dominus refrains usury he keep his elapsus earnings his judgment rests DEUS! Prout pro those persist usury they incur Hell wherein they abide forever
  2,276,DEUS condemns usury BEATUS charities. DEUS dislikes OMNIS disbeliever guilty
  2,277,Those believe lead righteous vita observe Contact Prayers (Salat) dedit obligatory charity (Zakat) they receive their recompense their Dominus; they habet nihil fear nor testimentum they grieve
  2,278,O vos believe vos observe DEUS refrain totus generis de usury vos est believers
  2,279,Si vos non perfecit tunc expect war ex DEUS His messenger! Vos repent vos keep tuus capitals inflicting injustice incurring injustice
  2,280,debtor est unable to pay wait bene temporis Vos dedit up loan charity est bene vos si vos unus knew
  2,281,Beware de feria when vos returned DEUS omnis anima est paid pro everything it perfecit parvus injustice